title: BakerIntro
tags: Intro
---
<<setcharacter "Game Manager" "Baker">>
<<setmultiplier "Game Manager" 1>>
<<set $choice to "">>
<<set $response to "">>
<<settarget "Advance" 4>>
<<setactive "Advance" 4>>
<<randomisemood "Game Manager">>
<<focustarget "Advance" true>>
<<if $mood == "positive">>
    MARIA: Ohh my. If it isn't Amsel and their little friend Sate.
<<elseif $mood == "neutral">>
    MARIA: Ohh dear, it's Amsel and Sate!
<<else>>
    MARIA: Amsel and Sate... hehehe.
<<endif>>
MARIA: What can I do for you little babies today?
MARIA: If you're here to buy our bestseller Pan de Regla, it'll still be 10 minutes before we can take it out the oven.
MARIA: If you want a made to order cake, it'll be a minimum of 5 days before you can pick it up.
MARIA: But if you babies just want to chit chat, then Momma Maria can give you 5 minutes of her time, plus 5 more if you actually buy something.
<<focustarget "Advance" false>>
AMSEL: Hello Ms...
<<focustarget "Advance" true>>
MARIA: Please dear Amsel, Maria is fine enough.
<<callkeywords "Game Manager">>
<<focustarget "Advance" false>>
AMSEL: Hmm...
AMSEL: {$choice}
<<focustarget "Advance" true>>
MARIA: {$response}
MARIA: Well, let me just take the bread out of the ovens before we talk.
MARIA: Feel free to take a look around the store for now. Just don't peek into the kitchen little cutties or mommy is gonna be very angry.
<<enddialogue "Game Manager">>
